Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.39,0:00:03.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,上一集的Love Live! Superstar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:06.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,隨著我與四季兩個新生加入
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:08.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Liella!成為了8人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.78,0:00:11.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,二年級的學姐果然都好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:12.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:14.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們試了各種方法想拉近跟學姐的差距
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:16.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但總是不太理想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.58,0:00:18.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看見這樣的我們的是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:19.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,鬼夏好~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.91,0:00:22.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一年級的鬼塚夏美
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.42,0:00:25.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,夏美表示想要擔任Liella!的製作人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:29.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是 她似乎還有著不可告人的目的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.88,0:00:32.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,團名…嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.97,0:00:34.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:37.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,難得我們4個能作為Liella!的姐妹團活動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:39.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,當然需要一個新的團名了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:40.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,例如…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:42.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(全力#)\N這個!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.14,0:00:43.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,全力#?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.27,0:00:45.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,例如…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:46.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(KIRARA!!)\N這個如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:48.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好像雜誌的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:51.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,再說我們也不是Liella!的姐妹團
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:54.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這 這我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.16,0:00:56.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想想…要說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:00:57.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是小組
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.95,0:00:59.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒錯 要取個小組名
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.99,0:01:02.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,僅限這個夏天的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.87,0:01:04.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小夏美
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:04.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:07.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們之所以要與學姐分開練習
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.84,0:01:10.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是因為想追上學姐們的腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.05,0:01:13.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為我們想成為Liella!的力量去爭奪優勝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:15.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好啦好啦 沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:16.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:16.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Liella!的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:19.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要是無法成為Liella!的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.60,0:01:21.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我就不打算當學園偶像了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:23.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,至少我是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.73,0:01:24.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Me too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:26.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這 這我也明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:29.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就只是一個提議 提議而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:32.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,比想像中還頑固呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.74,0:01:35.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還以為只要把人分開就能讓我隨心所欲了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:38.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過夏美是不會放棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:41.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼 我們重振精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:42.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今天就來拍攝各位的日常…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.63,0:01:48.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:51.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來 奮戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:55.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,掀起我們的旋風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:57.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,爬上巔峰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:01:58.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們絕不認輸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.93,0:02:00.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要拿下勝利!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:10.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不夠 還不夠 遠遠不夠!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:13.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不論何時我都要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:16.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,超越昨天的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:19.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,究竟能走到哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.16,0:02:20.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然仍舊不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:21.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還是要燃燒自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:24.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想與你一同歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:27.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想了解尚未知曉的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:30.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我還會更加成長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:32.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不想輕易放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:36.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:38.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,現在立刻 Start up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:41.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,向頂點前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:44.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還要更加 更進一步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:47.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,更加情緒高昂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:50.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去實現吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:52.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在這瞬間 盡自己所能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:55.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,追尋夢想 盡自己全力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:03:00.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為邂逅 給了我熱情的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:03.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:07.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就算是不可能的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:08.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也去實現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:11.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們會繼續相信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:14.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒錯 WE WILL!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:21.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,安安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:22.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:25.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:28.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我旁邊那位把氣氛弄得很沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:32.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這時候就輪到兒時玩伴出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:35.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:41.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我在想我們到底哪裡做錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:42.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,做錯了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:45.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,難得一年級的都加入了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:49.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還以為暑假可以大家一起開開心心練習的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:51.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她們不是也說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:54.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們並沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:56.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:01.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她們都說了想自己練習看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:06.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我認為那是件很棒的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:07.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:08.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:10.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,默默等待她們回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:12.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也是我們這些學姐該做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:15.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們也要繼續提升實力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,成為Galaxy的目標啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:21.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,而且暑假結束後就要地區預賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:23.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在那之前還有學園祭喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.79,0:04:29.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(#06 Dekkaidow!)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:32.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,歡迎來到希奈子的故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:33.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:35.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過這裡還真是不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:37.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,環境清幽 空氣新鮮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:39.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,食物也很美味喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:41.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼就先跑到希奈子家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:42.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:45.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:47.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼 妳不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:50.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們決定要在希奈子家集訓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:54.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,彎不回去…都是那輛巴士害的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:56.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:57.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但為什麼連我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:05:00.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為妳說要攝影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:01.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳還說只要是為了製作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:03.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,無論什麼地方都會跟我們去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,貼身跟拍記錄下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:05.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:08.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那就是我的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:10.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,該說那只是場面話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:11.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還是我沒想到會這麼誇張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:14.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,幫妳墊的交通費
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:15.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:18.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Money…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:20.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,僅次於我性命 重要的money…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:23.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,接下來要一路跑到小希奈子家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:29.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:31.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跑步機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:38.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等 等等…!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:40.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小希奈子的家在哪邊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:41.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:42.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:43.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,回轉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:45.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,快停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:47.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是怎樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:54.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好乖好乖 都長這麼大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:55.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:56.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:59.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:03.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳們到底還要練到怎樣才滿意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:04.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:07.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,畢竟我們決定要成為Liella!的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:08.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就算這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:12.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,牠叫妳打起精神來喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.06,0:06:13.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳居然懂喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:14.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:17.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好了 換完衣服就來練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:35.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:40.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,謝謝妳們特地來這一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:41.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不要客氣儘管吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:44.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看起來好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:46.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好大的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:48.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,畢竟我們家是開民宿的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:51.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,非常適合作為集訓地點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.35,0:06:54.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,話說回來 小夏美好慢喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:57.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她剛剛好像在房間裡的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:06:59.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,鬼夏好~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:04.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今天要向大家介紹鬼夏風夏日精力冰沙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:07.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.35,0:07:10.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,冰沙的影片完全賺不到錢\N(活力滿分 鬼夏風夏日冰沙)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:13.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那就只好把今天的練習影片加工一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:15.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(超人氣學園偶像 Liella! 內鬨!?)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:18.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,再弄得刺激點或許比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:20.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(超人氣學園偶像 Liella! 即將解散!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.13,0:07:25.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過影片內容就只是在練習而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:26.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,管他的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:28.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,反正這樣就能讓觀看次數暴增
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:30.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Money也會跟著滾滾來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:32.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,"Liella! 即將"…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:34.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:37.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,什麼也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:38.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:39.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,已經要吃飯囉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:41.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我馬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:43.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,剛剛太專心剪片了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:45.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是我們今天練習的影片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:47.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不是 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:49.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒什麼好看的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:50.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:51.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是這個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:54.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是學姐們的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:56.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我在想能不能用來宣傳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:59.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這個舞台真的很厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:02.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,呃 對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:04.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也跟小芽衣她們聊過了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:07.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們的夢想就是要超越這個舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:08.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,夢想?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:12.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們加入之後就多了一年級的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:14.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以我們要能夠超越這個舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:17.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,讓Liella!的力量升級
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:19.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那就是妳們的夢想?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:22.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小夏美的夢想又是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:23.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:25.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳是CEO對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:27.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳的目標是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:31.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我沒什麼…特別的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:35.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,硬要說的話 就是賺很多錢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:37.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:38.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還問為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:41.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,當然是為了讓自己老了之後不用煩惱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:45.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好 我要去吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:47.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳先過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:08:59.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真是的 無聊透頂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:03.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(突襲! Liella!練習的樣子!)\N(IN北海道!)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:04.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:07.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這個 認真是認真的嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:09.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:10.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來這麼有人氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:13.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,而且留言也是一片好評
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:14.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以我才說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:16.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不必覺得難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:18.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,應該積極上傳影片才對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:20.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:21.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,完全沒在聽我說話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:24.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣學妹們或許就能有點自信了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:27.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過 可不一定全是好事喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:30.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,如果因此自信過頭的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:38.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳們幾個 不要給我站在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:41.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,從今天開始妳們就是伴舞了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:42.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:43.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:46.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,性格這麼扭曲的人只有堇而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:47.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,吐槽太隨便了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:48.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,比起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:51.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我更在意那個叫夏美的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:53.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她會特地來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:55.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我認為肯定是另有企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:58.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也是一直很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:02.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,應該要找夏美學妹好好問清楚才對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:04.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是她們人在北海道喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:05.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小千認為呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:08.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我沒在聽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:09.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:12.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我只是在想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:14.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,既然她們已經能做到這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:16.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為了幫她們增加自信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:19.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,把練習難度調高也不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:24.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Love Live! Superstar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:30.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我的夢想是將來在奧運拿下金牌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:33.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小夏美又是最後一名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:34.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我的夢想是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:37.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,成為拿到諾貝爾獎的科學家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:43.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我的夢想是成為模特兒環遊世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:46.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,完全長不高…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:53.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好討厭的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:10:58.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟學姐們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:10:59.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跳一樣的舞步?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:02.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我等等把詳細動作傳過去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:03.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,記得看喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:04.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:06.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,由於這的確會給妳們帶來壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:09.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以我本來想之後再找妳們商量的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:12.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但看過那部影片後我認為應該沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:13.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:17.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,當然 這對現在的妳們應該還很困難
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:18.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.45,0:11:20.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要暑假期間好好努力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:23.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,肯定能在學園祭前練好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:24.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:25.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:27.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要大家都達到同個等級
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就能增進所有人的自信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:32.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也能使我們更積極面對Love Live
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:35.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有個目標也比較容易規劃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:36.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是沒錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:39.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,畢竟我們的目標是Love Live優勝嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:40.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:42.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們會盡力的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:50.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,爸爸?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:55.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,忘記了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:12:00.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然影片得到好評讓人很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:02.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過練習的難度也提升了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:05.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,千砂都學姐這麼做太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:07.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明明我們才剛開始練習而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:10.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,鬼夏好~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:13.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是你的心靈鬼之補品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:15.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,鬼塚夏美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:16.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今天也要繼續為大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:19.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,帶來Liella!的練習影片喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:22.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們還沒開始練習啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:24.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣看起來會像是在偷懶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:27.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,實際上就是在偷懶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:29.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:30.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有很多原因的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:33.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我都聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:35.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,從外面就聽得見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:37.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:40.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳們的夢想是要超越那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:46.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳們的夢想應該是超越學姐們的舞台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:47.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,既然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:50.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就該負起責任才對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:50.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:52.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣就想放棄的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.46,0:12:54.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也不想再聽妳們談什麼夢想了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:58.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我在拍攝影片時是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:03.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳們的夢想決不是無法實現
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:04.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:08.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒錯 那是件非常美好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:14.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,擁有一個只要努力或許就能觸及的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:15.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小夏美…!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:23.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼 我們就繼續拍攝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:14.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,洗澡水的溫度還可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:15.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,剛剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:17.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:20.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不會 該道謝的是我才對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:23.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,白天真的很謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:28.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也沒說什麼了不起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:30.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:32.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,希奈子覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:37.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小夏美真的好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:39.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有個目標很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:42.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我不是說我沒有目標嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:43.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳太謙虛了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:45.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要是沒有目標
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:47.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,又怎麼會當CEO呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:50.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就說了我真的沒有什麼目標啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:54.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是因為真的沒有目標
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:55.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我才會像現在這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:59.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,除了賺money就沒什麼事能做了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:02.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:04.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,接下來我自己弄就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:05.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:09.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒聽見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:11.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:22.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是 是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:26.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這次又是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:28.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,四季同學? 還是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,熊…是熊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:34.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,該…該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:36.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要直接衝回民宿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:38.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不 這樣不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:39.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不可能跑得過牠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:39.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還是要裝死?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.92,0:15:42.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不行 聽說那根本就沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:47.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是我 是我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:49.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳 妳是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:57.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,其實我是來把我爸爸忘記的東西帶給他的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:15:59.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,打扮成熊送來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:02.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是那時爸爸給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:03.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,難得都來這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:05.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想說也給大家一點慰問品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:08.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要對東京的大家保密喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:11.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真是的 妳就這麼在意團員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:13.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那是當然的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:15.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也一樣在意小夏美喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:17.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:21.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我稍微聽到了妳跟小希奈子的談話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:22.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:23.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:25.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,反正也沒說什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:27.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:30.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就請香音學姐也來影片裡露個臉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:32.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣一來…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:33.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,比起那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:34.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳要不要來當學園偶像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.81,0:16:40.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我希望小夏美來當Liella!的第9位成員
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:44.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,完全搞不懂妳為什麼要說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:45.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:48.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,既然妳沒有夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:51.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要不要試著跟大家一起追逐同個夢想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:52.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,夢想?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:55.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,如果小夏美妳沒有夢想的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:00.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:01.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:04.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我曾經擁有過許多夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:07.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也已經明白夢想是不會實現的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:09.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟香音學姐這種
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:12.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看得到夢想的人是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:14.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也受過了許多挫折喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:18.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我本來有個夢想是進入結丘的音樂班
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:20.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,最後卻以失敗告終了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:24.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是 小可可跟大家教了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:28.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要跟大家一起 就有辦法努力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:33.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要互相彌補缺點跟不足之處
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.95,0:17:36.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就能夠一起追逐夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:40.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:45.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟著我做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:47.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:48.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別問了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:17:58.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:17.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 感覺很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:20.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們要整齊劃一地跳出這些舞步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:23.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在為我們加油的大家面前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:34.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這麼一來 坐在觀眾席的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:37.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也會在心中一同起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:40.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,整座舞台將合而為一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:43.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那正是最棒的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:48.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為大家帶來這樣的演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:50.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是我們的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:51.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,夢想…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:11.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,鬼夏好~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:13.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是你的心靈鬼之補品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:15.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,鬼塚夏美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:17.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒想到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:20.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是結女的學園祭喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:23.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不不不 就說別拍我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:24.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,交給妳了 小戀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:27.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好的 請大家盡情享受喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:30.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今年的演唱會我們更加有幹勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:34.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,比起這個 跟鬼夏的契約最後怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:35.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:37.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不用擔心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:38.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,畢竟夏美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:40.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,已經是Liella!的一員了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:43.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣真的好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:45.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼還在說這種話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:48.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,集訓時明明都練習那麼多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:50.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不如說妳是最賣力的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:52.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼要開始囉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:19:58.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這就是9個人的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:01.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,全新的Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:03.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,1!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:04.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,2!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:05.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,3!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:06.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,4!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:07.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,5!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:07.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,6!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:08.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,7!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:09.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,8!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.35,0:20:10.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,9!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:12.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們今天要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:15.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,盡情享受!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:37.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,用特技表演縱身一躍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:39.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跳過湛藍的大海
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:40.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,擊掌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:43.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,無論什麼都能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:45.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Vivid季節
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:49.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,淘氣模式發動中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:51.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以就別客氣了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:54.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,夏天是稍縱即逝 Happy的 最棒的Showtime
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:56.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一同起舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.52,0:20:58.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Clap your hands☆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:00.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗨起來吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:03.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,盡情玩樂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:07.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒玩個盡興就太遜·太遜·太遜了~!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:10.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Say Yeah Yeah Yeah Yeah~!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:11.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Funky coconut
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:14.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們是juicy的盛夏寵兒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:16.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,狀況十分良好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:19.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Heaven Heaven Heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:21.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Oh Babababy~!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:22.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Crazy coconut
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.97,0:21:24.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,浸染純白的心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.97,0:21:26.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Vitamin SUMMER!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:28.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,讓我嗨到最高點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:30.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Heaven Heaven Heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:32.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Yeah Yeah Yeah~!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:35.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Bababy~!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:38.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Yeah Yeah Yeah~!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.82,0:21:41.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Bababy~!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.66,0:21:51.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,感覺怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.87,0:21:54.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,…透了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:21:58.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真是…棒透了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.59,0:22:02.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好像找到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.63,0:22:06.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.97,0:22:12.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在我追逐的夢想前方 總是能看見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.68,0:22:15.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,名為希望的星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.89,0:22:20.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,正在閃爍著 閃爍耀眼光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.56,0:22:23.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,即便跌倒也能再次前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.19,0:22:28.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在我追逐的夢想前方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:33.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我究竟會走向何處呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.99,0:22:38.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,場場相遇之中 雖然又會迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.96,0:22:42.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請試著去享受這一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.46,0:22:45.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,覺得「似乎能做到卻做不到」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.59,0:22:47.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,最後做到的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:50.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就會很開心 想著要好好加油
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:54.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,整顆心都像是要跳了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.35,0:22:59.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,盡情歡笑 放聲高歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:01.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想傳達給你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.40,0:23:05.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,繼續走向遠方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:07.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,世界廣闊無邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:10.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然也有景色會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:13.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但熱情會始終如一!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:17.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跨越許多後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:19.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想實現的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.50,0:23:23.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來吧 大家一起去實現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.50,0:23:28.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明天要彈奏出什麼樣的悸動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.63,0:23:32.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去改變未來吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:38.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,下集 UR 葉月戀
